metadata.name: L2EPass
metadata.description: The L2E Pass  is truly everything you need to succeed in the NFT world with a limited supply of 2222 passes available. With the Plug Pass you get full access to discords analysis and live market updates. This will include video guides and training walking you through buying NFTs and insight on what projects the team is looking to mint. Best part is you’ll have access to join calls with crypto trading experts, get whitelist access for upcoming projects, and every NFT Tool you need, all on one platform. The [L2E] pass is the only NFT you need to turn your ideas into cryptocurrency with our “learn 2 earn” concept
